    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks awesome on the road? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been treated with a lot of love over the years. It's the perfect companion for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it handles. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your next favorite car!",
