    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle offers a fantastic blend of performance and everyday practicality. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated metallic grey that still catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor door dings and light scratches typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats show minimal bolsters wear, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records that prove it has never missed an oil change. It has recently been fitted with new brake pads and a fresh set of tires, ensuring it\u2019s ready for the road immediately. If you are looking for a dependable, well-maintained driver that looks great and performs even better, this is the one.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary choice for those who demand both reliability and refined performance. Meticulously maintained and showing clear evidence of pride in ownership, this automobile offers a seamless driving experience complemented by a well-preserved interior and a robust mechanical profile. It stands as a testament to enduring engineering, providing a sophisticated balance of utility and prestige. We invite you to inspect this exceptional offering, which has been vetted to ensure it meets our professional standards for roadworthiness and aesthetic appeal.",
      "price": 34800.0,
