      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, making it the perfect choice if you're looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great cruising down the street. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you. I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love to find it a great new home\u2014feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
